commentary: Johnson to Shahriar Nafees, OUT Nafees is done by the slower one. A lovely change of pace and Nafees picked it up very late. He lunged out in the end and ended up stabbing it straight up in the air. Watson came in and took it around short-leg position. Australia tighten the screws.

commentary: Smith to Mahmudullah, no run tries the Tendulkar sweep almost behind the keeper but misses and is hit on the pad. The ball rolls behind the stumps. It was refered to third umpire who says not out
